name: Pattern studies - Typographic patterns #2
description:
This work is part of study on generative, interactive and animated patterns which explores the relation between simplicity and complexity.
This is a simple grid of "§" drawn with the 'Fascinate Inline' font, one is 'normal' the other is a reflexions. To explore you can move the mouse to rotate and move the the letter, click to re-scale the grid. Press any key to change the character used.
The font used is 'Fascinate Inline' by Astigmatic available under the Open Font License at https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Fascinate+Inline?query=Fascinate+Inline#glyphs
